text: "Here We Go Again" is a song by English drum and bass duo Sigma, featuring vocals from English singer Louisa. It was released on 29 March 2019 by 3 Beat Records as the seventh single from the duo's upcoming second studio album. The song peaked at number 98 on the UK Singles Chart. ==Charts== {| class="wikitable plainrowheaders" style="text-align:center" |- ! scope="col"| Chart (2019) ! scope="col"| Peak position |- |} ==References== Category:2019 singles Category:2019 songs Category:Sigma songs
